Most of these products are made from isopropyl alcohol or ethanol, with the addition of sealants such as carbomer (acrylic acid polymer) in the form of gel, or humidifiers such as glycerine in liquid or foam form, which makes it easier to use these devices and reduce the effects of the drying of the skin by alcohol.
